This paper deals with social media analysis and health-related labels, which falls under the category of social media analysis (cs.SI). The use of profile pictures to infer body weight involves computer vision techniques, which could fall under the category of computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV) or multimedia (cs.MM). The analysis of behavior and social networks could also fall under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) or social and information networks (cs.SD).
